EN: This battle was a brutal battlefield.

ZH: 他身负重伤，却依然坚持战场上。
EN: Despite his serious injuries, he still persisted on the battlefield.

ZH: 战场上的枪声震耳欲聋。
EN: The sound of gunfire on the battlefield was deafening.

